ID: PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?Musico ?NombreMusico ?Descripcion ?Inicio ?Genero WHERE{ ?Musico dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Spanish_musicians>; rdfs:label ?NombreMusico . ?Musico dbpedia-owl:abstract ?Descripcion. ?Musico dbpedia-owl:activeYearsStartYear ?Inicio. ?Genero dbpedia-owl:genre dbpedia:Pop_music. ID: PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX r: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX d: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?dier ?naam ?name ?status ?trend ?ordenaam ?thumb ?link WHERE { ?dier d:class r:Bird . ?dier d:conservationStatus ?status . ?dier d:conservationStatus "CR"@en . ?link foaf:primaryTopic ?dier . ?dier dbprop:ordo ?orde . ?orde rdfs:label ?ordenaam . OPTIONAL { ?dier d:thumbnail ?thumb } . FILTER ( lang(?ordenaam) = "nl" ) } ORDER BY ASC(?ordenaam) ASC(?trend)

FILTER ( lang(?nombreMusico) = "es" ) ?musico dbpedia-owl:activeYearsStartYear ?inicio . FILTER ( ( ( ( ?inicio > "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?inicio < "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) || ( ( ?fin > "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?fin < "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) ) || ( ( ?inicio < "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?fin > "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) ) ?musico dbpedia-owl:activeYearsEndYear ?fin . FILTER ( ( ( ( ?inicio > "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?inicio < "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) || ( ( ?fin > "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?fin < "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) ) || ( ( ?inicio < "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) && ( ?fin > "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) ) ) } }
